NG0239:2: shri a yuhpa ti ka la ru dra tan+t+ra b+h+ya ba kr-i ta tan+t+ra ra dza /
NG0239:4: dpal tshe bdag nag po drag sngags mngon du phyung ba'i rgyud kyi rgyal po /
NG0239:5: bcom ldan 'das dpal tshe bdag nag po phrin las
NG0239:6: thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa de la phyag 'tshal
NG0239:7: lo // 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NG0239:8: bcom ldan 'das chos thams cad lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i snying po can /
NG0239:9: rdo rje 'chang chen po'i rang bzhin de /
NG0239:10: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi mkha' dbyings rnam par dag pa'i klong */
NG0239:12: rang byung ma bsgribs par gsal ba'i gzhal yas khang na /
NG0239:13: 'khor dus gsum gcig pa'i sangs rgyas dang */
NG0239:14: sa la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams dang */
NG0239:15: nyid kyi ngo bo las sprul pa'i lam la gnas pa'i rig 'dzin rnams dang */
NG0239:17: nye bar gnas pa'i 'khor gshin rje'i gshed kyi dge 'dun du ma dang */
NG0239:18: khrag skyugs pa ma mo'i tshogs dang */
NG0239:19: khams gsum pa lha'i tshogs dang */
NG0239:21: phung byed mngag pa'i tshogs dang */
NG0239:22: ma skyes lam la lta ba'i tshogs dang */
NG0239:24: ba'i thugs rje chen pos thabs cig tu bzhugs so //
NG0239:25: de nas bcom ldan 'das la 'khor rnams 'dun par gyur nas gsol ba btab bo //
NG0239:26: lhun grub gdal ba'i pho brang nas //
NG0239:27: bde chen mnyam pa'i ngang nyid las //
NG0239:28: rdo rje 'chang ba rdzogs pa'i sku //
NG0239:29: sprul pas 'gro ba'i don mdzod cig / ces gsol to //
NG0239:30: de nas bcom ldan 'das dkyil 'khor rnams yongs su 'dun par gzigs nas /
NG0239:31: chos nyid mi g.yo ba las bzhengs nas /
NG0239:32: dbang du bsdu ba'i ting nge 'dzin la zhugs so //
NG0239:33: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad g.yos par gyur te /
NG0239:35: chem chem rab tu chem mo //
NG0239:36: 'khor thams cad rab tu brgyal bar gyur to //
NG0239:37: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis 'khor rnams la gzigs nas /
NG0239:38: nyid kyi rang bzhin 'di bstan to //
NG0239:39: e ma chos sku byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin las //
NG0239:40: rgyu rkyen med pa'i rang byung sems //
NG0239:41: thams cad 'byung ba'i snying po las //
NG0239:42: thams cad thugs rje'i shugs kyis sgrol //
NG0239:44: de nas 'khor de rnams rang gi rang bzhin mthong nas /
NG0239:45: sems yongs su grol bar gyur te /
NG0239:46: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje 'chang chen po la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0239:47: e ma rdo rje snying po khyod //
NG0239:48: snang stong gnyis med ye shes skus //
NG0239:49: sna tshogs sbyor ba rdzogs pa'i bdag / yin par
NG0239:50: bdag cag yongs mi rtog / rgyu rkyen med par
NG0239:52: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis rdo rje brdar gsor bas /
NG0239:53: 'jig rten gyi khams rab tu g.yos te //
NG0239:54: 'khor thams cad skrag nas rang rang gi srog gi snying po mdongs gsol du phul lo //
NG0239:55: bcom ldan 'das 'jam pa'i rdo rje des /
NG0239:56: srog gi snying po thams cad skye ba med pa'i
NG0239:57: dbyings nam mkha' drag po'i 'khor du bsdus te gcig
NG0239:58: tu dril lo / las thams cad sgra'i dang po'i dang po la bsdus te gcig tu dril lo //
NG0239:59: de nas nyid kyi rang bzhin las ma g.yos pa'i 'khor bcom ldan 'das 'jam dpal gzhon nu des /
NG0239:60: bcom ldan 'das la gsol ba 'di btab bo //
NG0239:61: kun gyi rang bzhin nyid las byung *//
NG0239:62: sems nyid rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod //
NG0239:63: mi rtog rang bzhin ting 'dzin las //
NG0239:64: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor dang *//
NG0239:65: phyag rgya chen po rdzogs par mdzod //
NG0239:67: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis bde bar mnyam pa'i ngang las bzhengs te /
NG0239:68: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis bskul bar dgongs nas /
NG0239:69: phyag rgya chen po rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor 'di gsungs so //
NG0239:70: rang bzhin chos sku mnyam nyid las //
NG0239:71: lhun gyis grub pa'i pho brang brtag / ye shes chen po'i gzhal yas khang *//
NG0239:72: kun 'byung mi g.yo brtan par gnas //
NG0239:73: gru bzhi sgo bzhi rin po che //
NG0239:74: rta babs twa ra rgyan rnams ldan //
NG0239:77: rus sbal glang chen stag gzig 'brug / zhing dang zhing chung thod pa sbrul //
NG0239:78: gnam lcags khro chu chu srin thog / rgyu ma'i gling bu keng rus brgyan //
NG0239:79: e yi pho brang thod mkhar bzhi //
NG0239:80: lcags mkhar bcu gnyis bcu drug ldan //
NG0239:81: khyams dang gru chad sgo bzhir ldan //
NG0239:82: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub par gnas //
NG0239:83: de la gnas pa'i phyag rgya'i sku //
NG0239:84: rgyal chen sa yi pho brang du //
NG0239:85: klu 'bum gnyan khri sa bdag stong *//
NG0239:86: lto 'phye phyogs skyong bzhi dang brgyad //
NG0239:87: ma he brgyad dang nyi zla'i gdan //
NG0239:88: nag po dug chen bskyil ba'i sku //
NG0239:89: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhir bgrad //
NG0239:90: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar mthing nag dbus //
NG0239:91: klu gnyan sa bdag zhing chung sbrul //
NG0239:92: 'khor lo ral gri rdo rje g.yas //
NG0239:93: be con gtun shing sdigs mdzub g.yon //
NG0239:94: glang chen zhing stod stag lpags smad //
NG0239:95: dbu la rin chen gzhal yas nang *//
NG0239:96: rigs bzhi klu brgyad thod pas mdzes //
NG0239:97: bdud srin mu stegs rgyal po btsan //
NG0239:98: mgo dang tsit+ta do shal byas //
NG0239:99: rin po che dang nor bus mdzes //
NG0239:100: snyan cha mgur chu phyag zhabs sbrul //
NG0239:101: bdud mo mthing nag thod sbrul brgyan //
NG0239:103: thugs kar gsod byed smug nag gcer //
NG0239:104: rigs bzhi'i rgyan dang thod pas mdzes //
NG0239:106: zhing dang sbrul dang lhu dum 'bul //
NG0239:107: ya ma'i thugs kar badzra ni //
NG0239:108: ljang nag rdo rje snying phreng bsnams //
NG0239:109: klu brgya'i gdan la gnyan khri gsol //
NG0239:110: rin chen dbu rgyan rigs bzhi'i mdzes //
NG0239:111: gdug pa 'joms mdzad dregs pa'i sku //
NG0239:112: dregs pa'i thugs kar rus sbal gnas //
NG0239:113: sme ba thig le khrag dang dug / mtshon cha'i spu la sder mo lcags //
NG0239:115: lha srin mi yi snying po 'chang *//
NG0239:116: dbu la bya khyung gdug pa 'dul //
NG0239:117: spu dang gshog pa mtshon cha me //
NG0239:118: mchu dang sder mo gnam lcags 'bar //
NG0239:119: nyi zla khro chu'i spyan dang tshems //
NG0239:120: gdug pa za zhing zhe sdang sbrul //
NG0239:121: phrag sor khyung mo smug nag gnyis //
NG0239:122: spu dang gshog pa mtshon cha me //
NG0239:123: gdug pa za zhing de bzhin 'brul //
NG0239:124: nu mar seng ge brjid pa gnyis //
NG0239:125: mtsho cha spu gri sder mo dbal //
NG0239:126: 'phrul gyi gshog pa khro chu'i so //
NG0239:127: dgra bgegs za zhing lhu dum 'phrul //
NG0239:128: sog par stag chen rngam pa gnyis //
NG0239:129: mche ba rtsang phur sder mo lcags //
NG0239:130: glo snying nang rol snying khrag 'thung *//
NG0239:131: sta zur zhe sdang gdug pa'i gzugs //
NG0239:132: dug sbrul me 'bar dug khrag zags //
NG0239:133: dug lnga brkam chags bsreg cing 'joms //
NG0239:134: gang dmigs rtsa khrag klad khrag 'thung *//
NG0239:135: dug sbrul rlangs pa dgra la 'phro //
NG0239:136: mgur dang zhabs kyi long bu'i bar //
NG0239:137: ye shes khro bo tshon gang ba //
NG0239:139: sur+ya'i gdan la phyi nang srung *//
NG0239:141: thams cad glo snying nang rol za //
NG0239:145: dbus na brkyang bskum tshul du bzhugs //
NG0239:146: thugs kyi sprul pa mngon phyung ba //
NG0239:147: mon pa dug chen dregs pa'i lus //
NG0239:148: dbu dgu phyag dgus tsit+ta bsnams //
NG0239:149: phyag dgus bla dang don snying khrag / drod dang dbang po lus srog 'bral //
NG0239:150: bdud bzhi pho nya las la bskul //
NG0239:152: dbugs srog bkrag mdangs tshe srog 'chang *//
NG0239:153: yum dang bcas pa thod mkhar bzhir //
NG0239:154: lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul du gnas //
NG0239:155: lcags mkhar phyogs bzhi'i gzhal yas na //
NG0239:156: srog gcod phyi yi mon pa gshed po bzhi //
NG0239:157: dug mda' lcags gzer gnag la 'tsher //
NG0239:158: khyab pa spyi bcings so bdar gnag / pho brang phyogs bzhir lhun gyis grub //
NG0239:159: lcags mkhar brgyad kyi khyams khang na //
NG0239:160: lus kyi sprul pa gshed po bzhi //
NG0239:161: yum dang bcas te tshogs brgyad 'joms //
NG0239:162: sgo med bcu drug lcags mkhar na //
NG0239:163: kam ka sha za dregs pa'i tshogs //
NG0239:164: mngag pa gzhan tshogs lhun gyis grub //
NG0239:165: dregs pa'i las dang sbyor ba'i grangs //
NG0239:166: bzhi dang bcu drug bcu gnyis brgyad //
NG0239:167: de bzhin lnga dang bcu drug brgyad //
NG0239:168: snying po don la bcu gnyis gsum //
NG0239:169: de yi snying po mchog bsdus lnga //
NG0239:170: dbang gi brtul zhugs bgrod dang lnga //
NG0239:171: de srog dam tshig gnyis dang gsum //
NG0239:172: chos nyid mi g.yo bsam gtan lus //
NG0239:173: rdzas dang 'dod pa bskul ba'i rkyen //
NG0239:174: srog dang las dang e ka la //
NG0239:175: bsdus nas rang dbang gtso la phul //
NG0239:176: byin rlabs ngar bcas thig ler bstim //
NG0239:177: sangs rgyas kun bdag de bzhin gshegs //
NG0239:178: rdzogs pa'i tshul du lhun gyis grub //
NG0239:179: drag sngags mngon du phyung ba'i rgyud las /
NG0239:180: khro bo gleng gzhi'i le'u ste dang po'o // //
NG0239:181: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis drag sngags 'byung ba'i
NG0239:183: rtsa ba mi 'gyur byang chub sems //
NG0239:184: gcig ni kun gzhi'i rang bzhin yin //
NG0239:185: chos kyi dbyings ni skye med pas //
NG0239:186: sangs rgyas sku gsum ye shes thugs //
NG0239:187: sems dang lus la bag chags brtas //
NG0239:188: snang dang srid pa'i chos rnams kun //
NG0239:189: byang chub sems dang dbyings su 'dus //
NG0239:190: mtshan mar mi gnas rang bzhin gcig / spros med bde chen dag pa'i sku //
NG0239:191: 'gag med rang bzhin dag pa'i gsung *//
NG0239:192: ma bsgrib don rnams rdzogs pa'i thugs //
NG0239:193: sems lus bag chags gsal ba dag / bde dang sdug bsngal gnyis kar snang *//
NG0239:194: don gcig byang chub sems las byung *//
NG0239:195: 'gro ba'i rgyud la bag chags las //
NG0239:196: rgyu rkyen skye med bag chags las //
NG0239:198: snang srid mi rtog rgyu rkyen bral //
NG0239:199: bde ba skye med ngang gis stong *//
NG0239:200: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu gcig tu gnas //
NG0239:201: chos sku mi gnas ye shes sku //
NG0239:202: don gcig rig pa yang dag 'brel //
NG0239:206: don dam kun rdzob gnyis su med //
NG0239:207: thabs dang shes rab phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0239:208: dbyings las ye shes rig pa yi //
NG0239:209: rang bzhin lhun grub phyag rgyar gsal //
NG0239:210: rgyud drug gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang *//
NG0239:211: mya ngan 'das pa'i sangs rgyas don //
NG0239:212: rgyu 'bras dbyer med chos skur gsal //
NG0239:213: ye shes rol pa'i phyag rgyar bstan //
NG0239:214: rang byung thugs kyi rol pa las //
NG0239:215: drag sngags ye shes rol par shar //
NG0239:216: ye shes bde ba'i thig le las //
NG0239:217: drag sngags thugs rje sprul par shar //
NG0239:218: chos sku bde ba'i dbyings nyid las //
NG0239:219: drag sngags sprul par rang byung shar //
NG0239:220: skye med rnam dag rang bzhin las //
NG0239:221: drag sngags skye ba'i cho 'phrul shar //
NG0239:222: sbyor ba kun 'byung rdzogs pa'i gzhi //
NG0239:223: drag sngags mngon du phyung ba'i rgyud las /
NG0239:224: drag sngags 'byung ba'i gzhi bstan pa'i le'u ste gnyis
NG0239:225: pa'o // // de nas yang bcom ldan 'das kyis
NG0239:226: chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang las /
NG0239:227: skye ba'i cho 'phrul drag po mngon du byung ba'i rtsa ba'i sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0239:228: drag po nye bar sbyor ba ni //
NG0239:229: dur khrod gnyan ri'i dben gnas su //
NG0239:230: 'brel pa gsum dang ldan pa yi //
NG0239:231: grogs dang dpa' brtul dmod pa bca' //
NG0239:232: de yi sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0239:233: nye bar gcig tu dril bsdebs pa'i //
NG0239:235: tshe srog bdag po ya ma dregs //
NG0239:236: srid pa'i khyams khang tsit+ta la //
NG0239:237: dngas ma bzhi dang si ra brgyad //
NG0239:238: rtsa bran drug dang brgyad gnyis phyi //
NG0239:239: mdud pa gsum dang srog shing gsum //
NG0239:240: ldan pa'i thig le 'od kyi tshul //
NG0239:241: sa chu me rlung nam mkha' dbus //
NG0239:242: pa thag tshon gang rang sgra'i 'od //
NG0239:243: kun 'dus snying po bcu gnyis gnas //
NG0239:244: dbus kyi nam mkha' skye med las //
NG0239:245: steng 'og dngas ma bag chags tshul //
NG0239:246: brten pa'i sbubs na dgyes dang bdud //
NG0239:247: drod kyi sbubs na ma gshin 'bru //
NG0239:248: chu yi sbubs na rus sbal dregs //
NG0239:249: rlung gi sbubs na me dang bskyed //
NG0239:250: kun gyi steng 'og rtsa dang rlung *//
NG0239:251: ye shes lnga yi 'od du gnas //
NG0239:252: mdud pa bzhi yi 'brel chen la //
NG0239:253: mi 'gyur rno dbal mtshon cha'i sngags //
NG0239:254: srog la gnyis dang breng shag gnyis //
NG0239:255: hur thum gnyis dang hri dza gnyis //
NG0239:256: srog 'phrog stobs kyis drag sngags gnas //
NG0239:257: phyi rim 'brel chen rtsa brgyad la //
NG0239:259: zhen bzlog gsang lam zug pa 'byin //
NG0239:260: thams cad gzir zhing rang gzir nas //
NG0239:261: yang logs bcu gnyis rgya mdud la //
NG0239:262: gdug pa'i snying gzer rdzogs par gnas //
NG0239:263: si ra bcu gnyis sbubs dag la //
NG0239:264: gab pa sngags kyi phreng bas gang *//
NG0239:265: de bzhin phyi yi bcu drug la //
NG0239:266: dbang sdud sngags kyi de bzhin gang *//
NG0239:267: dngas ma bzhi yi mtshams bzhi la //
NG0239:268: srog bzhi lo thog 'joms pa yi //
NG0239:269: drag sngags gnam lcags thog chen gnas //
NG0239:272: lha srin mi yi snying po sba //
NG0239:273: 'bru re bsdus nas gong bur gnas //
NG0239:274: de las yon tan du ma 'byung *//
NG0239:276: gang mos las la nye ba yi //
NG0239:277: nye bar gcig tu dril bsdebs pa'i //
NG0239:279: yang dag rtsa ba'i 'khor lo ste //
NG0239:280: zhing ras la sogs rgyu bzhi la //
NG0239:281: thig skor bzhi dang ldan par bskor //
NG0239:282: bar khyams sprul bcas rdzogs byas la //
NG0239:283: dbus la sogs pa'i phyogs bzhi dang *//
NG0239:284: de bzhin phyogs mtshams brgyad du brtag / srid pa'i khyams khang lto ba na //
NG0239:285: rgya gram rlung ri sbag mar gnas //
NG0239:286: dang po tshangs pa'i thig gnyis dang *//
NG0239:287: zur thig de bzhin cha mnyam la //
NG0239:288: dbus su gru gsum zla kham gsum //
NG0239:289: phyi rim phyogs bzhir rgya gram rwa //
NG0239:290: dbus kyi snying po phyogs bzhi la //
NG0239:291: 'khrul mig lcags mkhar gsum gsum gnas //
NG0239:292: rgya gram mtshams bzhir khrag gi mtsho //
NG0239:294: yang logs zlum po mu khyud chu //
NG0239:295: skyom zhing g.yeng ba sdud cing 'thibs //
NG0239:296: lto sbyor las kyi 'khor lo yin //
NG0239:297: yang logs dbus mtshams phyogs brgyad du //
NG0239:298: rlung ri rdo rje rtse mo re //
NG0239:299: snying po 'khrul mig gnyis gnyis ldan //
NG0239:300: las rnams rdzogs pa'i spu gri gnas //
NG0239:301: rlung ri gshed kyi 'khor lo yin //
NG0239:303: gsod byed drag po rngam pa yi //
NG0239:304: drag po las kyi 'khor lo yin //
NG0239:305: byang khram snying po spu gri sngags //
NG0239:306: rtsa ba gcig tu dril ba yin //
NG0239:307: gru gsum ming rus zla kham lha //
NG0239:308: bsrung ba kun ldan rdzogs par bri //
NG0239:309: rgya gram bzhi yi 'phrul mig la //
NG0239:310: rtsa ba'i snying po drag sngags dgod //
NG0239:311: 'khor yug rbad dang bsad pa'i sngags //
NG0239:312: gang bsgrub lto sbyor gnas mthun dgod //
NG0239:313: phyi rim rdo rje rtse brgyad la //
NG0239:314: ming gi 'bru gsum dang por bri //
NG0239:315: gsod cing gnon dang 'phen pa yi //
NG0239:316: spu gri so gsum rdzogs par dgod //
NG0239:317: mtsho gling bar khyams rwa dbus la //
NG0239:318: sdang dang gnod pa de bzhin bri //
NG0239:319: ming gi 'bru gnyis srog dang sbyar //
NG0239:320: gang 'dod mtshams su de bzhin blang *//
NG0239:321: b+hu ra na ga gdug pa'i ha la'i mtshon //
NG0239:322: b+hi la khong 'dus khong dregs can //
NG0239:323: 'bar ba ka li ya ma'i klong *//
NG0239:324: kyo ba kam b+ha gur b+ha sha / yam ram e du tsa ma d+hi //
NG0239:325: ma ra ya ni sbyor ba'i mchog / lto sbyor
NG0239:326: bcas la thod par gzhug / zhag bdun sngags sbyor
NG0239:327: sgrol ba dril // rus sbal pho mo'i 'khrul 'khor bca' //
NG0239:328: thod pa rgya gram rus sbal ltor //
NG0239:329: sbyor ba kun ldan klu la gtad //
NG0239:330: sngags kyi rtsa ba dril la brdeg / zhag gsum nyin gcig nyin zhag gnyis //
NG0239:331: gsad dang gnan pa zor gyi dus //
NG0239:332: rig pa bde bas ya ma'i klong *//
NG0239:333: 'khor la rtsa ba'i sbyor ba yin //
NG0239:334: drag sngags sbyor ba 'di lta ste //
NG0239:335: e ka he dun ya hri myag thum ril shag ya //
NG0239:336: dgra bo'i srog ma ra ya myog rbad /
NG0239:340: gsod pa drag po'i rtsa ba las //
NG0239:341: phrin las sbyor ba'i rgyal po yin //
NG0239:342: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis drag po'i sbyor ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0239:343: drag po mngon du phyung ba las //
NG0239:344: gsang chen sngags kyi dmod par dril //
NG0239:345: yang gsang chen po'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0239:346: dur khrod ras sam shing ras la //
NG0239:347: mu khyud bdun dang ldan par bskor //
NG0239:348: de la bri zhing dgod pa ni //
NG0239:349: dbus su gru gsum drag po las //
NG0239:350: brnag pa pho mo'i ming rus bri //
NG0239:351: zla kham bsrung ba de bzhin bri //
NG0239:352: mtshon cha'i 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi la //
NG0239:354: mtshon cha'i rgyal po bcu gnyis la //
NG0239:355: khro bo stobs kyi 'bru gcig dang *//
NG0239:356: tshe srog sdud pa'i snying po gcig / khong khrag 'brel ba'i 'bru lnga la //
NG0239:357: gsod cing gnon pa'i spu gri bcu //
NG0239:358: dgod pa'i gnas mthun lho sbyor dgod //
NG0239:359: phyi rim mu khyud bzhi po la //
NG0239:360: rigs bzhi sbrul gyi ra bas bsdam //
NG0239:361: lnga pa thod pa'i phreng bar gnas //
NG0239:362: drug pa sreg pa'i me ri 'bar //
NG0239:363: de dag tshe srog 'chang ba yi //
NG0239:364: rus sbal lto na gnas par bri //
NG0239:365: srid gsum lto na 'chang zhing gsod //
NG0239:366: tshe srog bdag po'i lto na yang *//

NG0239:2487: slob ma tshe bdag sku bsgom la //

NG0239:2495: byin brlabs brtul zhugs 'jug pa brtsam //

NG0239:2498: gsang ba lhun grub mkha' la 'jug / brtul zhugs sngon 'gro'i rim pa bdun //

NG0239:2500: rgyan cha phyag mtshan drag po'i dbang *//
NG0239:2501: gtor ma rak+ta bdud rtsi bstab //

NG0239:2517: dkyil 'khor dang bcas bdag cag mnyam pa yi //

NG0239:2525: mnyam pa'i rgyal po dgongs su gsol //

NG0239:2585: nyon mongs gcod pa'i ral gri dang *//

NG0239:2697: dmar len sngags kyi snying po zung *//

NG0239:2700: mtshan nyid bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o // //
